  "title": "Registered Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Close liaison with doctors to ensure delivery of high-quality patient care</li>\n  <li>Attend and follow up on patient enquiries</li>\n  <li>Perform nursing duties such as blood pressure taking, venepuncture and ECG</li>\n  <li>Dispense medicine in the course of business of the clinic</li>\n  <li>Perform clinic administrative duties such as coordinating of appointments, billing, update and maintain medical records while ensuring accuracy and patient confidentiality</li>\n  <li>Involve in inventory management and stock taking of medicine and apparatus used in the clinic</li>\n  <li>Respond to Code Blue and other urgent calls for care</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Registered nurse with Singapore Nursing Board (SNB)</li>\n  <li>Diploma in Nursing</li>\n  <li>Possess good command in English and effective communication skills</li>\n  <li>Great team player</li>\n  <li>Well versed in medical knowledge</li>\n  <li>Experience in private clinic setting and/or Cardiology setting will be an added advantage</li>\n</ul>",
